Interface INonProfit

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NonProfit
    public interface INonProfit
    Provides the functionality afforded to NonProfits, including the ability to calculate all donations received (or to be received) within a certain year. !!! Used emptySet, add, contains, and remove methods from HW 4 !!! (with slight modifications)
